God pardon them that are the cause of it!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 RIVERS\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 A virtuous and a Christian-like conclusion,\
To pray for them that have done scathe to us.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 GLOUCESTER\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 So do I ever:\
being well-advised.\
