\f0\b \cf2 GLOUCESTER\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 [Aside] So wise so young, they say, do never\
live long.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

