\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 CATESBY\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 He will do all in all as Hastings doth.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 BUCKINGHAM\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 Well, then, no more but this: go, gentle Catesby,\
