Give mistress Shore one gentle kiss the more.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 BUCKINGHAM\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 Good Catesby, go, effect this business soundly.\
